#summary TOC of expressions encountered with NUL

Expressions tree.

 * Knowledge related
  * NulKnowledge
  * NulPossible
 * Objects
  * Undefined objects
   * NulLocal - A local unknown value - a name bound to a knowledge.
   * NulIor3 - Several values that can be taken.
   * NulAttribute - The attribute of another object.
  * Defined objects
   * NulLitteral - An atomic meaningful given value.
   * NulSet - A pair of objects (base of sets and lists)
   * NulLambda - A value used to associate an object to another.
   * NulJsSet - Some !JavaScript hard-coded sets.
